        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Methane Emissions Research Act of 2023&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency to conduct a methane research pilot study to quantify methane emissions from infrastructure used for the production, gathering and boosting, processing, transmission, and storage of oil and natural gas in the United States.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
